object.script:
function onTick() Zoom = input.getNumber(5) GPSX = input.getNumber(6) GPSY = input.getNumber(7)
inputX = input.getNumber(3) inputY = input.getNumber(4) isPressed = input.getBool(1)
isPressingRectangle1 = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, (288-17), 3, 14, 14)
isPressingRectangle2 = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, (288-17), 20, 14, 14)
output.setBool(1, isPressingRectangle1) output.setBool(2, isPressingRectangle2) end
function isPointInRectangle(x, y, rectX, rectY, rectW, rectH) return x > rectX and y > rectY and x < rectX+rectW and y < rectY+rectH end
function isPointInRectangle(x, y, rectX, rectY, rectW, rectH) return x > rectX and y > rectY and x < rectX+rectW and y < rectY+rectH end
function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() h = screen.getHeight()
screen.drawMap(0, 0, Zoom)
screen.setColor(255, 255, 255, 255)
screen.drawText(3, 3, "GPS X:") screen.drawText(3, 10, "GPS Y:")
screen.drawText(35, 3, (GPSX*10^2-(GPSX*10^2)%10)/(10^2)) screen.drawText(35, 10, (GPSY*10^2-(GPSY*10^2)%10)/(10^2))
screen.setColor(255, 255, 255, 255) screen.drawRect((3), (17), 6, 51) screen.setColor(255, 0, 0, 100) screen.drawRectF((4), (68), 5, (-(Zoom)))
screen.setColor(255, 0, 0, 255) screen.drawCircleF(w/2, h/2, 2)
if isPressingRectangle1 then screen.setColor(255, 0, 0, 255) screen.drawRectF((w-17), 3, 14, 14) else screen.setColor(255, 255, 255, 255) screen.drawRectF((w-17), 3, 14, 14) end
screen.setColor(0, 0, 0, 255) screen.drawTextBox((w-16), 4, 13, 13, "C",0, 0)
if isPressingRectangle2 then screen.setColor(255, 0, 0, 255) screen.drawRectF((w-17), 20, 14, 14) else screen.setColor(255, 255, 255, 255) screen.drawRectF((w-17), 20, 14, 14) end
screen.setColor(0, 0, 0, 255) screen.drawTextBox((w-16), 21, 13, 13, "R-S",0, 0)
end

function onTick() -- Inputs Hour = input.getNumber(8) Minute = input.getNumber(9) Fuel = input.getNumber(10) FuelPerc = input.getNumber(11) RPS = input.getNumber(12) Throttle = input.getNumber(13) EngTemp = input.getNumber(14) Battery = input.getNumber(15) Heading = input.getNumber(16) Speed = input.getNumber(17) Temp = input.getNumber(18)
--Touch Screen inputX = input.getNumber(3) inputY = input.getNumber(4) isPressed = input.getBool(1)
isPressingRectangle1 = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, (288-17), 3, 14, 14)
isPressingRectangle2 = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, (288-17), 20, 14, 14)
output.setBool(1, isPressingRectangle1) output.setBool(2, isPressingRectangle2)
end
--TouchScreen Function function isPointInRectangle(x, y, rectX, rectY, rectW, rectH) return x > rectX and y > rectY and x < rectX+rectW and y < rectY+rectH end
--Rounding Function function PrecisionAdj(x,y) return (x*10^y-(x*10^y)%10)/(10^y) end function onDraw() w2 = screen.getWidth() h2 = screen.getHeight() screen.setColor(255, 255, 255, 255) --Time screen.drawText(3, 3, "Time:")
if Hour < 10 then screen.drawText(27, 3, "0") screen.drawText(32, 3, (string.gsub(PrecisionAdj(Hour,1).."","%.0",""))) else screen.drawText(27, 3, (string.gsub(PrecisionAdj(Hour,1).."","%.0",""))) end screen.drawText(37, 3, ":") if Minute < 10 then screen.drawText(42, 3, "0") screen.drawText(47, 3, (string.gsub(PrecisionAdj(Minute,1).."","%.0",""))) else screen.drawText(42, 3, (string.gsub(PrecisionAdj(Minute,1).."","%.0",""))) end --EngTemp screen.setColor(255, 255, 255, 255) screen.drawText(3, 10, "Engine Temp:") screen.drawText(63, 10, (string.gsub(PrecisionAdj(EngTemp,1).."","%.0",""))) --Temp screen.setColor(255, 255, 255, 255) screen.drawText(3, 17, "Temperature:") screen.drawText(63, 17, (string.gsub(PrecisionAdj(Temp,1).."","%.0",""))) -- Fuel Bar screen.setColor(255, 255, 255, 255) screen.drawRect((w2/3), 3, (w2/3), 10)
screen.setColor(155, 155, 155, 255) screen.drawRectF(((w2/3)+1), 4, (FuelPerc*((w2/3)-1)), 9)
if (FuelPerc*((w2/3)-1)) > 20 then screen.setColor(0, 0, 0, 255) screen.drawTextBox(((w2/3)+1), 4, (FuelPerc*((w2/3)-1)), 9, "Fuel",0, 0) else screen.setColor(255, 0, 0, 255) screen.drawTextBox(((w2/3)+1), 4, (w2/3), 9, "Fuel",0, 0) end
-- FuelNr screen.setColor(255, 255, 255, 255) screen.drawText((w2/3), 16, "Fuel:") screen.drawText(((w2/3)+25), 16, (string.gsub(PrecisionAdj(Fuel,2).."","%.0",""))) -- RPS screen.setColor(255, 255, 255, 255) screen.drawText((w2/3), 23, "Engine RPS:") screen.drawText(((w2/3)+54), 23, (string.gsub(PrecisionAdj(RPS,1).."","%.0",""))) -- Throttle screen.setColor(255, 255, 255, 255) screen.drawRect((w2/3)+70, 23, (w2/3)-70, 5) screen.setColor(100, 100, 100, 255) screen.drawRectF(((w2/3)+71), 24, (Throttle*((w2/3)-71)), 4) -- Speed screen.setColor(255, 255, 255, 255) screen.drawText((w2/3), 30, "Speed:") screen.drawText((w2/3)+29, 30, (string.gsub(PrecisionAdj(Speed,2).."","%.0",""))) --Battery screen.setColor(255, 255, 255, 255) screen.drawText((w2/3), 37, "Battery Charge:") screen.drawText((w2/3)+75, 37, (string.gsub(PrecisionAdj(Battery,4).."","%.0",""))*100) --Hdg screen.setColor(255, 255, 255, 255) screen.drawText((w2/3), 44, "Heading:") screen.drawText((w2/3)+40, 44, (string.gsub(PrecisionAdj(Heading,2).."","%.0",""))) -- Touch Button
if isPressingRectangle1 then screen.setColor(255, 0, 0, 255) screen.drawRectF((w2-17), 3, 14, 14) else screen.setColor(255, 255, 255, 255) screen.drawRectF((w2-17), 3, 14, 14) end
screen.setColor(0, 0, 0, 255) screen.drawTextBox((w2-16), 4, 13, 13, "M",0, 0)
if isPressingRectangle2 then screen.setColor(255, 0, 0, 255) screen.drawRectF((w2-17), 20, 14, 14) else screen.setColor(255, 255, 255, 255) screen.drawRectF((w2-17), 20, 14, 14) end
screen.setColor(0, 0, 0, 255) screen.drawTextBox((w2-16), 21, 13, 13, "R-S",0, 0)
end
